+pip install -r requirements.txt -r requirements-dev.txt
+uvicorn src.ecl.server.app:app --reload
+make evaluate
+```
+
+**5) Open a PR**
+Follow the PR template, keep commit messages Conventional Commit style, and link to the issue.
